trans-unit.source: Maintains the collection of sub-properties of a given parent <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry" />.
trans-unit.target: 維護給定父代 <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry" /> 之子屬性的集合。

trans-unit.source: The parent <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue" /> instance used for the initialization.
trans-unit.target: 用於初始化作業的父代<see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue" />執行個體。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntryCollection" /> class using the sub-properties of the specified <see cref="P:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntryCollection.ParentValue" /> instance.
trans-unit.target: 使用指定之 <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntryCollection" /> 執行個體的子屬性，初始化 <see cref="P:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntryCollection.ParentValue" /> 類別的新執行個體。

trans-unit.source: Gets the number of <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry" /> instances in this collection (typically the number of sub-properties for the parent <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue" />).
trans-unit.target: 取得此集合中的 <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry" /> 執行個體數目 (通常是父代 <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue" /> 的子屬性數目)。

trans-unit.source: An integer that specifies the number of instances in this collection.
trans-unit.target: 指定這個集合中執行個體數目的整數。

trans-unit.source: Returns an <see cref="T:Systems.Collections.IEnumerator" /> object that iterates all the <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry" /> instances in this collection.
trans-unit.target: 傳回 <see cref="T:Systems.Collections.IEnumerator" /> 物件，這個物件在此集合中逐一查看所有 <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry" /> 執行個體。

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerator`1" /> that can be used to iterate through the collection of <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry" /> instances.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerator`1" />，可用來逐一查看 <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry" /> 執行個體的集合。

trans-unit.source: The name of the property to get.
Gets a <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry" /> instance with the specified name from this collection.
trans-unit.target: 取得此集合中具有指定之名稱的 <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry" /> 執行個體。

trans-unit.source: It is used for sub-property retrieval.
trans-unit.target: 此執行個體用於擷取子屬性。

trans-unit.source: A property entry instance with the specified name; or <see langword="null" /> if it does not exist.
trans-unit.target: 含有指定名稱的屬性項目執行個體；如果不存在，則為 <see langword="null" />。

trans-unit.source: Gets the parent <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue" /> from the host infrastructure.
trans-unit.target: 取得主機基礎結構中的父代 <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue" />。

trans-unit.source: Returns an <see cref="T:Systems.Collections.IEnumerator" /> object that iterates all of the <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry" /> instances in this collection.
trans-unit.target: 傳回 <see cref="T:Systems.Collections.IEnumerator" /> 物件，這個物件在此集合中逐一查看所有 <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry" /> 執行個體。

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.Collections.IEnumerator" /> object that can be used to iterate through collection of <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry" /> instances.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Collections.IEnumerator" /> 物件，可用來逐一查看 <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry" /> 執行個體的集合。
